  "text": "Gal4(1-100), Med15 and Med15(107-255) were bacterially expressed and purified as previously described. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Peptides used in this study All peptides were synthesized on CLEAR amide resin (Peptides international) using standard HBTU/HOBT/DIEA solid phase peptide synthesis protocols as previously described. [CITATION_3] The TFA-cleaved peptides were precipitated with ether, purified by reversephased HPLC using a 0.1% TFA/CH 3 CN solvent system and verified by electrospray mass spectrometry.",
